Fuzz Face Calculator

Leakage Measurement:
- R1 Value (default = 2.2M)
- R2 Value (default = 2.472k)
- Voltage 1:

- Shows:
  - Estimated leakage current in uA (I_leakage = V1 / R2)
  - Perceived gain: (hFE_perceived = V1 * 100)

hFE Measurement:
- Voltage 2:

- Shows:
  - Adjusted Voltage (V_adj = V2 - V1)
  - hFE = V_adj * 100
  


